Karen Sillas https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Karen_Sillas 0 Karen Sillas (born June 5, 1963) is an American stage and film actress. She graduated from the Acting Conservatory of the State University of New York. She is also a speech coach. Karen_Sillas ( born June_5_,_1963 ) is an_American_stage_and_film_actress .
